OL,3,CHundreds of motorists caught drink-
OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,FThe figures relate to Driver and
OL,7,FVehicle Licensing Agency statistics
OL,8,Freleased in response to a freedom of
OL,9,Finformation request.
OL,11,FThey are a snapshot of the number of
OL,12,FDR10 endorsements on driving records
OL,13,Fon July 20.
OL,15,FThe endorsements ` which last for 11
OL,16,Fyears from the date of the offence `
OL,17,Fare given to motorists convicted of
OL,18,Fdriving or attempting to drive with
OL,19,Falcohol above legal limits.
