OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,FMotoring organisations said the
OL,7,Ffigures demonstrate the need for the
OL,8,FGovernment to consider introducing a
OL,9,Frequirement for alcolocks to be used
OL,10,Fin the UK.
OL,12,FThe devices ` which prevent a
OL,13,Fvehicle's ignition from starting
OL,14,Funless a person passes a breath test `
OL,15,Fare used in several European nations `
OL,16,Fsuch as France, Belgium, Italy and
OL,17,FDenmark ` as a possible alternative to
OL,18,Fdriving bans.
