OL,3,CHundreds of motorists caught drink-
OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,FPolice forces in England and Wales
OL,7,Fconducted around 229,000 breath tests
OL,8,Fin 2022, according to Home Office
OL,9,Ffigures.
OL,11,FThat was 11% more than the previous
OL,12,Fyear, but 16% below 274,000 in 2019,
OL,13,Fbefore the coronavirus pandemic.
OL,15,FDepartment for Transport (DfT) figures
OL,16,Fshow an estimated 300 people were
OL,17,Fkilled in crashes on Britain's roads
OL,18,Finvolving at least one driver over the
OL,19,Flegal alcohol limit in 2022.
