OL,3,CHundreds of motorists caught drink-
OL,4,Cdriving four times or more
OL,6,FThat was up from 260 the previous year
OL,7,Fand was the highest total since 2009
OL,8,Fwhen 380 were recorded.
OL,10,FThe drink-drive limit in England,
OL,11,FWales and Northern Ireland is 80mg of
OL,12,Falcohol in 100ml of blood.
OL,14,FNowhere else in Europe has a limit
OL,15,Fabove 50mg/100ml.
OL,17,FThe Scottish Government reduced its
OL,18,Flimit to that level in 2014.
